data.name: grdPaid.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,MAX(A.BUNHO) BUNHO ,MAX(A.ORDER_DATE) ORDER_DATE ,NVL(A.CHULGO_YN, 'N') JOJE_YN ,FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(A.BUNHO) SUNAME ,MIN(C.ORDER_REMARK) ORDER_REMARK ,MIN(C.DRG_REMARK) DRG_REMARK FROM DRG9041 C ,DRG2010 A WHERE A.ORDER_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_order_date) AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND A.ACT_DATE IS NULL ) OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND A.ACT_DATE IS NOT NULL ) OR (:f_gubun = '3' )) AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS1003 IS NULL AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') <> 'Y' AND A.PRINT_YN = 'Y' AND NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN,'N') = 'N' AND A.JUNDAL_PART = 'PA' AND A.FKOCS1003 IN (SELECT X.PKOCS1003 FROM OCS1003 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND X.PKOCS1003 = A.FKOCS1003) AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND C.BUNHO (+)= A.BUNHO AND C.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND :f_bunho IS NULL GROUP BY A.DRG_BUNHO, NVL(A.CHULGO_YN, 'N'), FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(A.BUNHO) UNION ALL SELECT A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,MAX(A.BUNHO) BUNHO ,MAX(A.ORDER_DATE) ORDER_DATE ,NVL(A.CHULGO_YN, 'N') JOJE_YN ,FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(A.BUNHO) SUNAME ,MIN(C.ORDER_REMARK) ORDER_REMARK ,MIN(C.DRG_REMARK) DRG_REMARK FROM DRG9041 C ,DRG2010 A WHERE A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND A.ACT_DATE IS NULL ) OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND A.ACT_DATE IS NOT NULL ) OR (:f_gubun = '3' )) AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS1003 IS NULL AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') <> 'Y' AND A.PRINT_YN = 'Y' AND NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN,'N') = 'N' AND A.JUNDAL_PART = 'PA' AND A.FKOCS1003 IN (SELECT X.PKOCS1003 FROM OCS1003 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND X.PKOCS1003 = A.FKOCS1003) AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND C.BUNHO (+)= A.BUNHO AND C.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE GROUP BY A.DRG_BUNHO, NVL(A.CHULGO_YN, 'N'), FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(A.BUNHO) ORDER BY 3 DESC, 1

data.name: grdOrderList.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT A.BUNHO BUNHO ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,A.NAEWON_DATE NAEWON_DATE ,A.GROUP_SER GROUP_SER ,A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,A.JAERYO_CODE JAERYO_CODE ,A.NALSU NALSU ,A.DIVIDE DIVIDE ,A.ORD_SURYANG ORD_SURYANG ,A.ORDER_SURYANG ORDER_SURYANG ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI', A.ORDER_DANUI) ORDER_DANUI ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('SUBUL_DANUI',A.SUBUL_DANUI) ,A.GROUP_YN GROUP_YN ,A.JAERYO_GUBUN JAERYO_GUBUN ,A.BOGYONG_CODE BOGYONG_CODE ,B.BOGYONG_NAME BOGYONG_NAME ,FN_DRG_LOAD_DRG0130(C.CAUTION_CODE) CAUTION_NAME ,A.CAUTION_CODE CAUTION_CODE ,A.MIX_YN MIX_YN ,E.ATC_YN ATC_YN ,A.REMARK REMARK ,A.DV DV ,A.DV_TIME DV_TIME ,A.DC_YN DC_YN ,A.BANNAB_YN BANNAB_YN ,A.SOURCE_FKOCS1003 SOURCE_FKOCS1003 ,A.FKOCS1003 FKOCS1003 ,A.FKOUT1001 FKOUT1001 ,A.SUNAB_DATE SUNAB_DATE ,B.PATTERN PATTERN ,C.JAERYO_NAME JAERYO_NAME ,NVL(a.SUNAB_NALSU,0) SUNAB_NALSU ,NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN,'N') WONYOI_YN ,D.ORDER_REMARK OCS_REMARK ,A.ACT_DATE ACT_DATE ,A.BUNRYU2 MAYAK ,A.TPN_JOJE_GUBUN TPN_JOJE_GUBUN ,NVL(C.MIX_YN_INP,'N') UI_JUSA_YN ,A.SUBUL_SURYANG SUBUL_SURYANG ,E.SERIAL_V SERIAL_V ,G.ORDER_REMARK ORDER_REMARK ,G.DRG_REMARK DRG_REMARK ,A.HUBAL_CHANGE_YN HUBAK_CHANGE_YN ,A.PHARMACY PHARMACY ,A.DRG_PACK_YN DRG_PACK_YN ,A.POWDER_YN POWDER_YN FROM DRG9042 G ,DRG2030 E ,OCS1003 D ,INV0110 C ,DRG0120 B ,DRG2010 A WHERE A.ORDER_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_jubsu_date, 'yyyy/mm/dd') AND A.DRG_BUNHO = :f_drg_bunho AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS1003 IS NULL AND A.JUNDAL_PART IN ('PA' , 'AC' , 'AT' , 'IR') AND B.BOGYONG_CODE(+) = A.BOGYONG_CODE AND C.JAERYO_CODE = A.JAERYO_CODE AND D.PKOCS1003 = A.FKOCS1003 AND E.JUBSU_DATE (+)= A.ORDER_DATE AND E.DRG_BUNHO (+)= A.DRG_BUNHO AND E.FKOCS1003 (+)= A.FKOCS1003 AND G.IN_OUT_GUBUN (+)= 'O' AND G.FKOCS (+)= A.FKOCS1003 AND G.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND E.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE ORDER BY E.SERIAL_V, A.FKOCS1003

data.name: cbxActor.UserSQL
data.value: -- DRG USER LIST SELECT '' USER_ID , '' USER_NM FROM SYS.DUAL UNION SELECT A.USER_ID , A.USER_NM FROM ADM3200 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND A.USER_GROUP = 'DRG' AND NVL(A.USER_END_YMD, '9998/12/31') >= SYSDATE ORDER BY USER_ID NULLS FIRST
